The Bitcoin SDK provides an interface to interact with Bitcoin blockchains using SegWit (P2WPKH) transactions. It supports wallet connectivity, transaction preparation, and balance checking, using the bitcoinjs-lib library for core functionality.Wallet setupTo generate new Bitcoin WIF (Wallet Import Format) private keys for P2WPKH wallets, you can use the following tools:Bitcoin Tools (testnet)Bitaddress.orgGet tokens on the testnetFor testing process, you can use following links to get token on the testnet CoinfaucetTestnet FaucetInitializationImport the SDK and create a new instance:Copyimport { BTC } from "@kynesyslabs/demosdk/xm-websdk"

